OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FThe government has started announcing
OL,7,Fwhat political boundaries in the
OL,8,FMidlands will be expanded as part of
OL,9,Fits overhaul of local government in
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FIt wants to simplify local government
OL,13,Fby replacing the current system of
OL,14,Fdistrict councils with unitary
OL,15,Fauthorities, to operate in a similar
OL,16,Fway to Birmingham City Council and
OL,17,FShropshire Council.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FIt includes making changes to ten
OL,7,Fcouncils across Leicester,
OL,8,FLeicestershire and Rutland with a
OL,9,Fsmaller number of larger unitary
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FThese new councils would deliver all
OL,13,Fmajor services, including education,
OL,14,Fadult and children's social care,
OL,15,Fhighways, planning, waste collection,
OL,16,Fhousing and leisure.
OL,18,FNew unitary authorities in
OL,19,FStaffordshire and Stoke-on-Trent and
OL,20,FWarwickshire have also been proposed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FHere's a guide on the changes, the
OL,7,Fproposals are and what they mean.
OL,9,FLeicester City Council
OL,11,FThe government has announced it's
OL,12,Fopting for two unitary councils for
OL,13,Fthe area ` one covering an expanded
OL,14,FLeicester and one serving the rest of
OL,15,FLeicestershire and Rutland.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FThe city council will expand its
OL,7,Fboundary for the first time in more
OL,8,Fthan 50 years, absorbing Great Glen,
OL,9,FOadby, Wigston, Blaby, Enderby,
OL,10,FBraunstone Town, Glenfield, Anstey,
OL,11,FBirstall and Syston.
OL,13,FThis would increase Leicester's
OL,14,Fpopulation from around 372,000 to
OL,15,F623,000.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FThe council argues the expansion is
OL,7,Fneeded to accommodate around 30,000
OL,8,Fnew homes by 2046 and would save
OL,9,Faround #46 million a year through
OL,10,Freduced duplication and back-office
OL,11,Fefficiencies.
OL,13,FThe remainder of Leicestershire would
OL,14,Fbecome a single rural unitary
OL,15,Fauthority.
OL,17,FSir Peter Soulsby, Mayor of Leicester,
OL,18,Fsaid: " I'm very pleased about the
OL,19,Fgovernment's announced.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"It is the case that the government
OL,7,Fhas listened to the case that we've
OL,8,Fmade for the people in the wider
OL,9,FLeicester area who have independence
OL,10,Fand a stake in the city to have a vote
OL,11,Fin the city and to be able to shape
OL,12,Fits future.
OL,14,F"I'm pleased for them, I'm obviously
OL,15,Fvery pleased because, as the
OL,16,Fgovernment said, it opens up the
OL,17,Fprospect of providing housing that is
OL,18,Fdesperately needed in our city,
OL,19,Fpromoting the economy of the city,
OL,20,Fpromoting the growth of the city.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"And creating councils both in the
OL,7,Fcity and wider county area that are
OL,8,Ffinancially strong and stable."
OL,10,FAmanda Hack, Labour MP for North West
OL,11,FLeicestershire, said: "The new
OL,12,Fcouncils announced today will make it
OL,13,Feasier for local people to hold
OL,14,Fdecision-makers to account, while
OL,15,Fcreating streamlined structures that
OL,16,Fsupport faster, more efficient
OL,17,Fdecisions on infrastructure and public
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,26,@sD@WOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"Together, this will deliver better
OL,7,Foutcomes, better value for taxpayers
OL,8,Fand pave the way for a devolution deal
OL,9,Fthat can unlock Leicestershire's full
OL,10,Fpotential."
OL,12,FA new North Derbyshire Council will
OL,13,Fcomprise of Bolsover, Chesterfield,
OL,14,FDerbyshire Dales, High Peak, North
OL,15,FEast Derbyshire.
OL,17,FThere will be 21 parishes from Amber
OL,18,FValley, while a new South Derbyshire
OL,19,FCouncil will be made up of Derby,
OL,20,FErewash, South Derbyshire as well as
OL,21,F14 parishes from Amber Valley.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FAdam Thompson, Labour MP for Erewash,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is an exciting new
OL,8,Fchapter, not just for Erewash and
OL,9,FDerbyshire but for the whole of our
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,F"Life will be made simpler for
OL,13,Fresidents with just one council to
OL,14,Fcontact when they are in need, and the
OL,15,Fcutting of bureaucracy will mean more
OL,16,Fmoney into the services we all depend
OL,17,Fon.
OL,19,F"I a proud to be part of a Labour
OL,20,FGovernment delivering on its promise."
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU{D@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
