SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FNottinghamshire
OL,8,FUrban areas of Broxtowe, Gedling and
OL,9,FRushcliffe will be brought into a new
OL,10,FGreater Nottingham Council, with the
OL,11,Fremaining areas making up the new
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Council.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FNeghat Khan, leader of Nottingham City
OL,7,FCouncil, said: "This is a significant
OL,8,Fmoment for Nottingham and the wider
OL,9,Fcounty, recognising the reality of
OL,10,Fthousands of people crossing local
OL,11,Fauthority boundaries every day for
OL,12,Fwork and school, or visiting family
OL,13,Fand friends, while acknowledging the
OL,14,Fdistinct identities of rural
OL,15,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"This shake-up will create brand new
OL,7,Fcouncils that are financially
OL,8,Fsustainable, more accountable to the
OL,9,Fresidents they serve and better
OL,10,Faligned to the way people live their
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,F"It gives us the best opportunity
OL,14,Fgrow, improves services and deliver
OL,15,Fthe best for our residents in the
OL,16,Fyears to come."
OL,18,FA spokesperson for all nine councils
OL,19,Fsaid: "The government has today
OL,20,Fannounced its preferred option for
OL,21,Flocal government reorganisation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"All nine councils have worked hard to
OL,7,Fmeet the deadlines set by central
OL,8,Fgovernment and to provide submissions
OL,9,Fthat we believe are best for the
OL,10,Fresidents we serve.
OL,12,F"We will continue to work together to
OL,13,Fensure services continue and that
OL,14,Fresidents and businessesJremain our
OL,15,Fpriority.
OL,17,F"We know this decision will generate
OL,18,Fsignificant reaction, especially in
OL,19,Fthe media.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"We want to reassure everyone that
OL,7,Fthis will not affect the day-to-day
OL,8,Frunning of your local council, our
OL,9,Fservices
OL,11,Fwill continue and we are working
OL,12,Fclosely with the thousands of staff
OL,13,Fwho are coming on this LGR journey
OL,14,Fwith us.
OL,16,F"The work has only just begun, and we
OL,17,Fcan now start the work of
OL,18,Ftransitioning to beJready by April
OL,19,F2028"
OL,21,FLincolnshire
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FNew Greater Lincoln and Lincolnshire
OL,7,FCouncils will be formed, with an
OL,8,Fexpanded city as one UA and the
OL,9,Fremaining areas joining together as a
OL,10,Fsecond - while North East Lincolnshire
OL,11,Fand North Lincolnshire remain in their
OL,12,Fcurrent form.
OL,14,FNaomi Tweddle, leader of City of
OL,15,FLincoln Council, said: "The time has
OL,16,Fcome to overhaul the outdated two-tier
OL,17,Fcouncil system so we can go further
OL,18,Fand faster in delivering for our
OL,19,Fresidents.
OL,26,@wD@XOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"The money it will save taxpayers can
OL,7,Fgo towards funding the frontline
OL,8,Fservices we deliver, and it will bring
OL,9,Fan end to the complex system where one
OL,10,Fcouncil is in charge of your bins and
OL,11,Fthe other roads.
OL,13,F"For Lincoln, having a unitary
OL,14,Fauthority on a slightly bigger
OL,15,Ffootprint will allow our city to
OL,16,Fretain its distinct identity as well
OL,17,Fas reach its potential ` it is a great
OL,18,Fstep forward."
OL,20,FStaffordshire
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FThe government has decided that two
OL,7,Fnew councils will cover Staffordshire
OL,8,Fand Stoke-on-Trent in the future.
OL,10,FA new unitary council covering the
OL,11,Fnorth of Staffordshire including
OL,12,FNewcastle-under-Lyme, Stoke-on-Trent
OL,13,Fand Staffordshire Moorlands. This is
OL,14,F494,803 people.
OL,16,FA new unitary council covering the
OL,17,Fsouth of Staffordshire including
OL,18,FStafford, East Staffordshire, Cannock
OL,19,FChase, Lichfield, Tamworth and South
OL,20,FStaffordshire. This is 682,775 people.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FUnder the government's timetable, the
OL,7,Fnew councils are expected to be
OL,8,Festablished in April 2028, with
OL,9,Felections to shadow councils held in
OL,10,FMay 2027.
OL,12,FThe two new unitary councils will
OL,13,Freplace Staffordshire and Stoke-on-
OL,14,FTrent's ten existing county, city,
OL,15,Fdistrict and borough councils.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G18/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FThere will be no immediate changes to
OL,7,Fcouncil services, and day-to-day
OL,8,Fservices such as household waste
OL,9,Fcollection, street cleaning, parks and
OL,10,Fhighways maintenance, children's
OL,11,Fservices and adult social care will
OL,12,Fcontinue to be provided as normal.
OL,14,FCouncillor Martin Murray, chair of
OL,15,FStaffordshire Leaders Board, said:
OL,16,F"Councils across the area have
OL,17,Fexpressed different views through this
OL,18,Fprocess, but the government has made
OL,19,Fits decision clear, and we are focused
OL,20,Fon making it work for Staffordshire
OL,21,Fand Stoke-on-Trent.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G19/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"We already have strong and well-
OL,7,Festablished partnerships, and all
OL,8,Fcouncils are united in our commitment
OL,9,Fto a smooth transition with no
OL,10,Fdisruption to the services residents
OL,11,Frely on.
OL,13,F"This is a significant and complex
OL,14,Fprogramme, but we will put residents
OL,15,Ffirst, protect essential services, and
OL,16,Fwork together to deliver a system that
OL,17,Fworks for the people we serve."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G20/24
