OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FJane Ashworth, leader of Stoke-on-
OL,7,FTrent City Council, said: "We warmly
OL,8,Fwelcome the government's decision to
OL,9,Fback the North-South proposal.
OL,11,F"It is the option that most closely
OL,12,Freflects the reality of how people
OL,13,Flive, work and travel across our area
OL,14,Fand provides the strongest basis for
OL,15,Ffuture success.
OL,17,F"The North-South model works with the
OL,18,Fgrain of our communities rather than
OL,19,Fagainst them.
OL,26,@oD@[OUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G21/24
