OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34122
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"It keeps North Staffordshire together
OL,7,Fas a single economic area, aligns with
OL,8,Fthe way key public services already
OL,9,Foperate and creates a council that is
OL,10,Flarge enough to be resilient while
OL,11,Fremaining rooted in the communities it
OL,12,Fserves.
OL,14,F"Most importantly, this decision gives
OL,15,Fus the opportunity to unlock growth,
OL,16,Fattract investment, accelerate
OL,17,Fregeneration and create more
OL,18,Fopportunities for local people.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G22/24
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34123
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784209691
OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,F"It will ensure north Staffordshire
OL,7,Fhas a stronger voice and can compete
OL,8,Fmore effectively for jobs, funding and
OL,9,Finvestment in the years ahead.
OL,11,F"Today's announcement is a significant
OL,12,Fmilestone, but the focus now turns to
OL,13,Fdelivery.
OL,15,F"We will work closely with our
OL,16,Fpartners, residents, businesses and
OL,17,Fstaff to ensure a smooth transition
OL,18,Fand to build a new authority that
OL,19,Fdelivers excellent services and a
OL,20,Fbrighter future for north
OL,21,FStaffordshire."
OL,26,@sD@AOU
