OL,3,CMajor shake-ups in local government
OL,4,Cbeing announced across the Midlands
OL,6,FWarwickshire
OL,8,FThe new North Warwickshire council
OL,9,Fwill serve North Warwickshire,
OL,10,FNuneaton & Bedworth, and Rugby. The
OL,11,Fnew South Warwickshire council will
OL,12,Fserve Warwick and Stratford-on-Avon.
OL,14,FWorcestershire
OL,16,FA new North Worcestershire Council
OL,17,Fserving Bromsgrove District, Redditch
OL,18,FBorough and Wyre Forest District
OL,19,Fareas. A South Worcestershire Council
OL,20,Fserving Malvern Hills District,
OL,21,FWychavon and Worcester areas.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G24/24
